---
title: Skeleton Loader
description: Animated placeholder loading state using CSS keyframes.
slug: skeleton-loader
cssFile: skeleton-loader.css
explanation: The shimmer effect uses a gradient as the <code>background</code> with a very wide <code>background-size</code> (200%). Animating <code>background-position</code> sweeps the lighter band across the element. Each skeleton element is just a <code>&lt;div&gt;</code> with rounded corners — the animation makes them all shimmer in sync.
---
{% extends "example.njk" %}
{% block demo %}
<div style="display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center">
	<div class="skeleton-card">
		<div class="skel skel-avatar"></div>
		<div class="skel skel-line w-full"></div>
		<div class="skel skel-line w-3q"></div>
		<div class="skel skel-line w-half"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="skeleton-card">
		<div class="skel skel-avatar"></div>
		<div class="skel skel-line w-full"></div>
		<div class="skel skel-line w-3q"></div>
		<div class="skel skel-line w-half"></div>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block html_code %}
{%- highlight "html" %}
<div class="skeleton-card">
  <div class="skel skel-avatar"></div>
  <div class="skel skel-line w-full"></div>
  <div class="skel skel-line w-3q"></div>
  <div class="skel skel-line w-half"></div>
</div>
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}

{% block css_code %}
{%- highlight "css" %}
.skel {
  background: linear-gradient(
    90deg,
    #f0f0f5 25%,
    #e0e0ea 50%,
    #f0f0f5 75%
  );
  background-size: 200% 100%;
  border-radius: 6px;
  animation: shimmer 1.5s infinite;
}

.skel-avatar { width: 44px; height: 44px; border-radius: 50%; }
.skel-line   { height: 12px; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
.w-full  { width: 100%; }
.w-3q    { width: 75%; }
.w-half  { width: 50%; }

@keyframes shimmer {
  0%   { background-position: 200% 0; }
  100% { background-position: -200% 0; }
}
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}
